      <li>Sending you newsletters, mailings, and information about programs,
        initiatives, activities, and events by e-mail or another medium;</li>
      <li>Processing your grant application or employment application;</li>
      <li>Event or program registration;</li>
      <li>Optimizing or improving our programs, services, and operations;</li>
      <li>Research and development;</li>
      <li>Verifying your account and account activities;</li>
      <li>Detecting, investigating, and preventing activities that may violate
        our policies or be illegal;
      </li>
      <li>Performing statistical, demographic, and marketing analyses of users
        of the Website and their usage patterns; and</li>
      <li>Managing our organization</li>
    </ul>

