      information in, the United States. The Bapatla Foundation shall not be
      liable under any circumstances for damages resulting from use of
      information collected from visitors to the Website.</p>
    <p>We reserve the right to modify or amend the terms of this Privacy Policy
      from time to time without notice. Your continued use of our Website
      following the posting of changes to this Privacy Policy will mean you
      accept those changes.</p>

